title: Kielsen II Cabinet
text:
The Second Cabinet of Kim Kielsen is the incumbent <a href="Government%20of%20Greenland">Government of Greenland</a>, in office since 2 February 2016. It is a <a href="coalition">coalition</a> <a href="majority%20government">majority government</a> consisting of <a href="Forward%20%28Greenland%29">Siumut</a>, <a href="Democrats%20%28Greenland%29">Demokraatit</a> and <a href="Atassut">Atassut</a>.
List of ministers.
The Social Democratic Siumut has 5 ministers including the Prime Minister. The Social liberal Democrats has 2 ministers. The Liberalistic Solidarity has 2 ministers.
